    <description
  >For Cases that were originally converted from Lead Opportunities, this will recreate the Lead Opportunity from the Case.
10/1/2025 LF (v5): Updated Lead Opportunity&apos;s default Close Date to 12/31 of the current year</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>f_Lead_Detail_2</name>
